metadata.name: Specie I ☆ﾟ٩(＾◡＾)۶☆ﾟ
metadata.description: This art explores the mix between fashion x fantasy x human sexuality, and comes around pastel pink tones and really sharp silver accesories, showin the beauty behind the pain and how this is connected to the wildness. Special thanks for Matieres Fecales and Poison Corp. for the inspo. The character was made on Daz Studio with ZBrush sculpting, all accessories self-made by Cryptoquariux on Procreate + ZBrush SVG extraction.
